**Title 和 PK 列完全可以同时保留**，这是 SharePoint 的标准做法：`Title` 是 SharePoint list 的强制 primary display column，你自己的 `EmployeeID` / `BatchID` 等是你 app 的 relational key，两者职责不同，不冲突，也不需要删掉任何一个。

以下是完整的 `scrManager` 设计，所有 bug 已修入。

---

# `scrManager` — 完整设计

## Screen 本体

**Name**
```
scrManager
```

**Fill**
```powerapps
RGBA(245,246,248,1)
```

**LoadingSpinner**
```powerapps
LoadingSpinner.Data
```

**OnVisible**
```powerapps
Refresh(PolicyEvents);
Refresh(EmployeeScopes);
Refresh(Batches);
Refresh(BatchLines);

Set(
    varUserEmail,
    Lower(Trim(User().Email))
);

ClearCollect(
    colPolicyEvents,
    Sort(
        Filter(
            PolicyEvents,
            Status = "Ready" || Status = "Draft"
        ),
        ScheduledTime,
        SortOrder.Ascending
    )
);

Set(
    varSelectedPolicyEventID,
    If(
        CountRows(Filter(colPolicyEvents, Status = "Ready")) > 0,
        First(Filter(colPolicyEvents, Status = "Ready")).PolicyEventID,
        If(
            CountRows(colPolicyEvents) > 0,
            First(colPolicyEvents).PolicyEventID,
            Blank()
        )
    )
);

Set(
    varSelectedSystemCode,
    LookUp(
        colPolicyEvents,
        PolicyEventID = varSelectedPolicyEventID,
        SystemCode
    )
);

ClearCollect(
    colManagerScopes,
    AddColumns(
        SortByColumns(
            Filter(
                EmployeeScopes,
                Lower(Trim(ManagerEmail)) = varUserEmail &&
                ActiveFlag = true &&
                SystemCode = varSelectedSystemCode
            ),
            "EmployeeName", SortOrder.Ascending,
            "TargetTA",     SortOrder.Ascending,
            "Environment",  SortOrder.Ascending
        ),
        SelectedAction, "No Change"
    )
);

Set(
    varManagerName,
    If(
        CountRows(colManagerScopes) > 0,
        First(colManagerScopes).ManagerName,
        User().FullName
    )
)
```

